{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"alias":"tactful-biophilic-xraytetra","creation_channel":"cli","description":"## Context\nGitHub Code Quality (CodeQL quality suite, public preview → GA/paid 2026-07-20) surfaced 631 Standard findings + 6 AI findings on the mirror. A 5-way triage (per-rule, cross-checked against ruff) classified them: 374 dismiss (false-positive/non-shipping/intentional), 230 low-priority 'present' (style/uniformity, deferred), and 27 genuine low-risk/low-effort fixes. Plus 4 mechanical AI test-cleanups. This ticket lands ONLY the 31 mechanical, no-behavior-change fixes as a single change.\n\n## Scope (31 fixes)\n- py/file-not-closed → wrap open() in a `with` (3 shipping: _store/ensures.py x2, _io/export_ndjson.py; + tests/scripts).\n- py/unnecessary-lambda → pass the callable directly (2 shipping: audit/page.py, _snapshot/janitor.py; + tests).\n- py/repeated-import → remove redundant function-local re-import (2 shipping: attest/opcert.py, llm/structured.py; + tests).\n- js/unused-local-variable → delete unused const (insertionProvider.js).\n- 4 AI test-cleanups: redundant local imports; split chained `and` assertions (test_editor.py, test_validation_depth.py).\n\n## Out of scope\nThe 374 dismissals (tracked separately for UI dismissal) and 230 'present' items (Pass 3 prioritization).\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- [ ] All 31 fixes applied; each is a mechanical transform with no behavior change.\n- [ ] `make lint` (ruff check + format) passes.\n- [ ] Affected test modules pass (targeted pytest run) + no import/collection errors.\n- [ ] Single Gerrit change; lands only after LLM-Review +1 AND Verified +1.","id":"dfc3-a0e9-93ab-4b5a","parent_id":"","priority":3,"tags":["code-quality","codeql","cleanup","chore"],"ticket_type":"task","title":"Remediate low-risk GitHub Code Quality preview findings (Pass 2)"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1784426171774524001,"uuid":"3887878e-17e4-44c6-8c81-bce5547bff54"}